Package org.semanticweb.rulewerk.core.reasoner.implementation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSourceConfigurationVisitor
    A visitor to generate (reasoner-specific) configuration for the various data sources.
    ReasonerDataSource
    An interface for DataSources that can be used with a Reasoner.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvFileDataSource
    An CsvFileDataSource stores facts in the CSV format inside a file of the extension .csv.
    EmptyQueryResultIterator
    Iterator that represents an empty query result.
    FileDataSource
    A FileDataSource is an abstract implementation of a storage for fact terms in a file of some format.
    InMemoryDataSource
    A DataSource for representing a large number of facts that were generated in Java.
    QueryAnswerCountImpl  
    QueryResultImpl

    RdfFileDataSource
    An RdfFileDataSource stores facts in the RDF N-Triples format inside a file of the extension .nt.
    Skolemization
    A class that implements skolemization and collision-free renaming of named nulls.
    SparqlQueryResultDataSource
    A SparqlQueryResultDataSource provide the results of a SPARQL query on a given web endpoint.
    TridentDataSource
    Data source for loading data from a database created with the Trident RDF indexing and storage utility.
